<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>HEAVENLY SUNLIGHT</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thangvan sunni vakin ka lam a salh,
 Dam-leh-guom hawh a ka zinna ah;
 Isu'n ei tiem, ei nutsieh ngeiloh ding,
 Pathien thutiem chuh a zuou ngei puoi.

[V2]
 Thangvan sunni vak (2)
 Pathien lopina'n ka tha ahih dim;
 Hallelujah! kipahna'n ka dim,
 Pahchak la ka sai Isu kei a.

[V3]
 2. Ka chiehna kimvel thimna'n tuom mah leh,
 Ka hukdampa mel a lieh thei puo'i;
 Amah Vak ahi, thimna a um thei puoi,
 Ei kitawnpih ina lamtawn in.

[V4]
 3. Thangvan In zuon in ni chengin ka chieh,
 Lamtawn in A pahchak la ka sa'i;
 A vak in ei salh, kipak in ka chieh,
 Thangvan Sunni Vak Isu kei a.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>402</hymn_number>
</song>